# No Emojis in Notifications

**Strict rule:** Never use emojis in any notification content — not in the `title`, not in the `body`, not anywhere the user sees a push notification banner.

## Applies to

- `notificationService.js` — schedule lineup notifications
- `trackingService.js` — new episode / chapter / release notifications
- Any future file that calls `Notifications.scheduleNotificationAsync` or similar

## Examples

- Bad: `title: '📺 New Episode!'`
- Good: `title: 'New Episode'`
- Bad: `title: '🎬 Release Day!'`
- Good: `title: 'Release Day'`

Keep notification text **clean, plain, professional** — no emojis, ever.
